{"data":[{"date":"10:10 08/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Spartak Moscow 0h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/nhan-dinh-paok-vs-spartak-moscow-0h00-ngay-98-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PAOK vs Spartak Moscow l\u00fac 0h00 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Spartak Moscow 0h00 ng\u00e0y 98 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh PAOK vs Spartak Moscow 0h00 ng\u00e0y 98 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/nhan-dinh-PAOK-vs-Spartak-Moscow-cup-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PAOK vs Spartak Moscow</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>PAOK vs Spartak Moscow: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2, PAOK \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng vang khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n t\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League, Basel (Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9) sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee5y S\u0129, PAOK \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 t\u1edbi 3-0. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Hy L\u1ea1p. C\u1ea7n nh\u1edb Basel t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng cho \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y khi g\u1eb7p Spartak Moscow c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Basel, PAOK d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u1eeda \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110\u00a0Nga. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fd do g\u00ec c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch quan nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1edbi PAOK? C\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Basel \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i sa s\u00fat qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Spartak Moscow s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec t\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 7 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG\u00a0Nga m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. L\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Hy L\u1ea1p, Spartak c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1edd v\u1eady, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2127","checkdouble":"194010"},{"date":"10:49 08/08","title":"M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2014/8/bongda24h-2014858189885.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Man United v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Mourinho.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh gia nh\u1eadp Old Trafford. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Bild &ndash; m\u1ed9t trang b\u00e1o kh\u00e1 uy t\u00edn t\u1eeb \u0110\u1ee9c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho Mourinho. Anh chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vinh h\u1ea1nh khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n sang Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Man United\" title=\"MU v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Boateng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/mu-van-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-boateng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ngu\u1ed3n tin n\u00e0y l\u1eadp lu\u1eadn, s\u1edf d\u0129 Boateng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Man United, b\u1edfi anh nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. X\u00e9t tr\u00ean b\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng Bayern Munich v\u00e0 PSG &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1edbn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u1eefa. T\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y mai (h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng), Man United v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam 1 trung v\u1ec7, v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Harry Maguire, Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Toby Alderweireld.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, Maguire l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Mina, h\u1ecd \u0111ang trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn tay ba v\u1edbi Everton. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ph\u00eda Everton nh\u1eafm ho\u1eb7c Mina, ho\u1eb7c Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh M.U trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i &ndash; Toby Aalderweireld d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean x\u00e9t trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Man United &ndash; r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-alderweireld-an-dut-maguire-172-194004.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/huyen-thoai-mu-alderweireld-an-dut-maguire.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-alderweireld-an-dut-maguire-172-194004.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Alderweireld \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t Maguire</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 Rio Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u00e0n em thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-pogba-co-the-da-trung-ve-172-194003.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mourinho-pobga-co-the-da-trung-ve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-pogba-co-the-da-trung-ve-172-194003.html\">Mourinho: Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1... trung v\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nHLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi m\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Man Utd \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2126","checkdouble":"194011"},{"date":"10:44 08/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Arsenal chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/arsenal-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-chambers.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir. Ch\u00ednh HLV Bruno Genesio \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fekir \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u CLB \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, Nabil Fekir thi\u1ebfu ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool. H\u1ecd v\u00e0 Lyon v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd v\u00e0 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c Fekir \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho Lyon ch\u01b0a v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng b\u00e1n. Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Man United v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ligue 1 mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/lyon-de-ngo-kha-nang-ban-nabil-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Fekir ra \u0111i b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLyon m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup. H\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m sau khi h\u00f2a 0-0 \u1edf 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh. Sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Bruno Genesio c\u1ee7a \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed s\u00f4ng Rhone\u201d kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc li\u1ec7u Fekir c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i \u1edf m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Ai m\u00e0 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra? C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Fekir v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Lyon.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho-172-194013.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-khung-bayern-chinh-thuc-tu-choi-man-united-172-194011.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-khang-dinh-se-khong-mua-them-nguoi-172-194007.html\">Pep kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jan-oblak-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-chelsea-172-194006.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-alderweireld-an-dut-maguire-172-194004.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Alderweireld \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t Maguire</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2125","checkdouble":"194012"},{"date":"10:54 08/08","title":"Sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Jerome Boateng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u1edd Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U nh\u1eafm Boateng n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Jerome Boateng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Jerome Boateng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Co-hoi-de-MU-mua-Jerome-Boateng-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Boateng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Mina t\u1eeb Barca b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i va ch\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Boateng gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f2i 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Boateng b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/that-bai-vu-mina-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-nguoi-thay-the-172-193829.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mua Jerome Boateng</span> \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u1edd Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jerome Boateng\" title=\"Jerome Boateng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0608-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U v\u00ec Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Mouirnho, anh c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBoateng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Mourinho v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng anh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Boateng, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Bayern quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2124","checkdouble":"194013"},{"date":"11:15 08/08","title":"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o \u1edf Arsenal khi\u1ebfn HLV Emery lo l\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/vi-tri-nao-o-arsenal-khien-hlv-emery-lo-lang-nhat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Arsenal l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 HLV Unai Emery c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Arsenal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Trong Top 7 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed3i nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 51 b\u00e0n thua.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 Arsenal  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 Arsenal  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/vi-tri-nao-o-arsenal-khien-hlv-emery-lo-lang-nhat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 trung v\u1ec7 m\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3, \u00f4ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua trung v\u1ec7\u00a0m\u1edbi. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Sokratis t\u1eeb Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sokratis t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Arsenal l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 HLV Unai Emery c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jerome Boateng\" title=\"Jerome Boateng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/ngay-hom-nay-88.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jerome Boateng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Laurent Koscielny \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-chambers-172-194012.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal chia tay Calum Cham</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Mustafi, Sokratis, Rob Holding v\u00e0 Konstantinos Mavropanos, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal quan t\u00e2m Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u1edbn. Domagoj Vida c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 quan t\u00e2m, Besiktas \u0111\u00f2i 29 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV PSG \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch mua s\u1eafm, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00f4ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Welbeck, Ospina v\u00e0 Lucas Perez l\u00e0 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i cao nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2123","checkdouble":"194014"},{"date":"11:12 08/08","title":"HLV Lyon m\u1eddi m\u1ecdc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia mua Nabil Fekir","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/lyon-de-ngo-kha-nang-ban-nabil-fekir.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir. Ch\u00ednh HLV Bruno Genesio \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fekir \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u CLB \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, Nabil Fekir thi\u1ebfu ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool. H\u1ecd v\u00e0 Lyon v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd v\u00e0 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c Fekir \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho Lyon ch\u01b0a v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng b\u00e1n. Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Man United v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ligue 1 mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/lyon-de-ngo-kha-nang-ban-nabil-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Fekir ra \u0111i b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLyon m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup. H\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m sau khi h\u00f2a 0-0 \u1edf 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh. Sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Bruno Genesio c\u1ee7a \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed s\u00f4ng Rhone\u201d kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc li\u1ec7u Fekir c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i \u1edf m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Ai m\u00e0 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra? C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Fekir v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Lyon.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho-172-194013.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-khung-bayern-chinh-thuc-tu-choi-man-united-172-194011.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-khang-dinh-se-khong-mua-them-nguoi-172-194007.html\">Pep kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jan-oblak-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-chelsea-172-194006.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-alderweireld-an-dut-maguire-172-194004.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Alderweireld \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t Maguire</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2122","checkdouble":"194015"},{"date":"10:57 08/08","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 8/8: Trung v\u1ec7 Boateng ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/ngay-hom-nay-88.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (8/8). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)\r\n<h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Boateng ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U</h2>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin ph\u00e1t \u0111i t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn Mourinho kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi bu\u1ed3n l\u00f2ng, b\u1edfi MU \u0111ang b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Bild cho hay, ngay sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa Bayern vs MU h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 22,3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 88, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 88, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0608-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jerome Boateng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda so v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Bayern y\u00eau c\u1ea7u (45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), b\u1edfi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Boateng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao ch\u00f3t v\u00f3t h\u01a1n 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, sau hai ng\u00e0y suy ngh\u0129, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Boateng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho Mourinho \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Red Devils.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o 17h ng\u00e0y 9/8 (gi\u1edd Anh). Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, Mourinho v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u00edt th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7 \u01b0ng \u00fd.<br>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\nPh\u00f3ng vi\u00ean t\u1edd Marca (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) v\u1eeba ghi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa Arrizabalaga l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay t\u1edbi London t\u1eeb s\u00e2n bay Madrid. Trong \u00edt gi\u1edd n\u1eefa, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Chelsea. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kepa, Chelsea ph\u1ea3i chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Athletic Bilbao. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Kepa s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Chelsea, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 66,9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng do Alisson Becker thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u khi gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga-172-193984.html\">N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Bournemouth ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Lerma</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c \u201c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u201d, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf \u1edf Premier League c\u0169ng b\u1ea1o chi \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Bournemouth cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ch\u1ecbu chi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jefferson Lerma t\u1eeb Levante v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua con s\u1ed1 k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan Nathan Ake t\u1eeb Chelsea n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Jefferson Lerma n\u0103m nay 23 tu\u1ed5i. Anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Colombia \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 88 Trung v\u1ec7 Boateng ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 88 Trung v\u1ec7 Boateng ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-88-Trung-ve-Boateng-phu-phang-tu-choi-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Leicester nh\u1eafm 2 trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\nThe Times cho bi\u1ebft, Leicester City \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 hai trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Caglar Soyuncu (Freiburg) c\u00f9ng Filip Benkovic (Dinamo Zagreb) v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 33,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Harry Maguire c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8.\r\n<h2>Real t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Modric</h2>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf t\u1ea1i Madrid, Marca ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Real Madrid \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Luka Modric d\u1ee9t \u00e1o sang Inter Milan. 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Los Blancos l\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara (Bayern Munich), Christian Eriksen (Tottenham) v\u00e0 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic. Trong \u0111\u00f3, tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Thiago \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 thi nh\u1ea5t, v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1eabn vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayern b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u00ednh \u201cn\u1ed5 bom\u201d ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i</h2>\r\nMundo Deportivo, t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n Barcelona  kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ousmane Dembele tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi  th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n  ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng  l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb d\u01b0\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-tung-chieu-doc-so-huu-dembele-khien-barca-nga-ngua-172-193969.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/arsenal-tung-chieu-doc-so-huu-dembele-khien-barca-nga-ngua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-tung-chieu-doc-so-huu-dembele-khien-barca-nga-ngua-172-193969.html\">Arsenal tung chi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Dembele khi\u1ebfn Barca ng\u00e3 ng\u1eeda</span><br>\r\n<span>Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Barca.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham h\u1ecfi mua Grealish</h2>\r\nTheo Sky Sports, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Aston Villa v\u1edbi hi v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jack Grealish. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra.\r\n<h2>Bayern ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thanh l\u00fd</h2>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Arturo Vidal nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Bayern Munich v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac, do v\u1eady gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Thiago Alcantara, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 Sebastian Rudy, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a RB Leipzig c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2121","checkdouble":"194016"},{"date":"11:19 08/08","title":"Real th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 Juventus v\u00e0 Roma: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/real-truoc-mua-201819-dau-roi-nhung-ke-khoc-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng kh\u00f3c th\u00fat th\u00edt gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Julen Lopetegui.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ho\u00e0i nghi gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e3 thua Man United 1-0 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 M.U c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Real, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m trong suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Julen Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i ngay, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan ng\u1ea1i s\u00e2u s\u1eafc cho Real, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb th\u00f9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Real \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U h\u00f4m 1/8 v\u1eeba qua bao g\u1ed3m Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 201819 \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 201819 \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Real-truoc-mua-201819-Dau-roi-nhung-ke-khoc-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e3 thua M.U 1-2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n sau World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t, \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng Toni Kroos, Marco Asensio, Isco c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 77 tr\u1edf \u0111i. Real h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh C trong hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBao tr\u00f9m l\u00ean \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Real \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd t\u1ecf ra m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so b\u00ec trong c\u00e1c pha tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng nhau trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n, tr\u1ea3i qua 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema ghi ban cho Real\" title=\"Benzema ghi ban cho Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Jose-Mourinho-nhan-xet-ve-Real-Madrid-va-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u00ec Real. C\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu Real thay 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a M.U ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00e2n l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 \u201cqu\u00e8 qu\u1eb7t\u201d l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eeba c\u01a1 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t sau 4 tr\u1eadn b\u1ebft b\u00e1t. Khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u201cC\u00e1o gi\u00e0\u201d l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng thua m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Bongda24h.vn ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n nh\u1eefng nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau kh\u00f3c. Ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u00e1c Madridistas. H\u1ecd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ra sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00e0o l\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, n\u00e0o l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n h\u1ecd\u2026 M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ef1c sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B thua \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu? N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh ch\u1eb3ng hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-vinicius-junior-180-192468.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-vinicius-junior.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-vinicius-junior-180-192468.html\">Thua M.U, HLV Real v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Vinicius Junior. \u00d4ng khen ng\u1ee3i sao tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man United t\u1ea1i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn?</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eb7p Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u201ctr\u00f9 \u1ebbo\u201d Real. R\u1ed3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 4-2 Barcelona, ch\u00fang l\u1ea1i vang l\u00ean nheo nh\u00e9o. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 reo vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u00e0ng th\u1eadt th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 l\u1eeda. Khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o gian kh\u00f3, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Real t\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U c\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ee9 gia v\u1ecb gi\u00fap c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1m ng\u01b0ng \u201cb\u1ed5n ph\u1eadn\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n mang l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid\" title=\"Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-juventus-real-van-rat-dang-so-du-khong-co-ronaldo.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus 3-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 AS Roma, Real \u0111\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 3-1 v\u00e0 2-1, h\u1ecd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ebf. C\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Real \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang t\u1edbi v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 suy gi\u1ea3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, trung b\u00ecnh Real ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng 65%, tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 28 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi 12 l\u00e0 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 43%. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real vs Roma Asensio ghi ban\" title=\"Real vs Roma Asensio ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Real-vs-Roma-Asensio-ghi-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Roma v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n Real t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u1ede gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, Los Blancos c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c hay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Luka Modric ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u1ede hai c\u00e1nh, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Marco Asensio, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ch\u1ea1m l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus v\u00e0 Roma, c\u1ea3 Bale v\u00e0 Asensio \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Real m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean khi 5 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Bale v\u00e0 Asensio v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 3 v\u00e0 2. N\u1ebfu Karim Benzema b\u00e9n duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n h\u01a1n, Real s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale toa sang tai Real\" title=\"Bale toa sang tai Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Bale-toa-sang-tai-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gareth Bale ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi 50 b\u00e0n/ m\u00f9a nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m. HLV Lopetegui c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t Ronaldo m\u1edbi b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Real ng\u1eebng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Eden Hazard khi Chelsea h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal c\u1ee7a Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch t\u00f4n vinh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0o, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Real ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1ea1o ra s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Juventus v\u00e0 Roma l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma, khi c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111a ph\u1ea7n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 (tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0o), h\u1ecd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid thang Roma\" title=\"Real Madrid thang Roma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/real-truoc-mua-201819-dau-roi-nhung-ke-khoc-muon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng lo nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n6 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Real tung ra v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Roma trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 l\u00e0 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i s\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m b\u00ean kia thay v\u00ec d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. C\u00f2n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i g\u00ec h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19 sau c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu? N\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft v\u1eabn r\u01a1i, n\u1ebfu v\u1eabn c\u00f2n than van, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 xem. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 cho tinh th\u1ea7n thi\u1ebfu cao th\u01b0\u1ee3ng!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/8/Real-2-1-Roma.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2120","checkdouble":"194020"},{"date":"11:29 08/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 08/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-0808.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 08/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9i thu cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0808 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0808 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0808-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018. T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1ee7a The Blues chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-hua-hen-ngay-cuoi-chuyen-nhuong-boi-thu-cho-chelsea-172-193991.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0808-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-hua-hen-ngay-cuoi-chuyen-nhuong-boi-thu-cho-chelsea-172-193991.html\">Sarri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9i thu cho Chelsea</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea. T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1ee7a The Blues chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Jan Oblak th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, theo El Correo c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zouma</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Kurt Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Bakayoko</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Kepa\" title=\"thu mon Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/chelsea-muon-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Athletic Bilbao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Batshuayi Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sevilla mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Michy Batshuayi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a c\u00f3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a c\u00f3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea cho Nantes m\u01b0\u1ee3n Matt Miazga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 2 m\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian va Mourinho\" title=\"Willian va Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Willian-va-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Mourinho \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi The Blues. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish, ng\u00f4i sao c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Spurs \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Blues trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m &quot;h\u00e0ng hot&quot; Bundesliga</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2119","checkdouble":"194021"},{"date":"11:30 08/08","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00f4ng tin th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng bongda24h t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Park Hang Seo.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong danh s\u00e1ch 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, &ldquo;ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o&rdquo; V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, so v\u1edbi 3 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh \u1edf 3 tuy\u1ebfn. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Olympic Uzbekistan kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Indonesia. \u00d4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u00f9ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Dang-Van-Lam-bi-loai-khoi-danh-sach-du-ASIAD-Ai-la-ke-that-bai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tay ngang, th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1eabn l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng &ndash; m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Park Hang Seo. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ngo\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay t\u1ea1i AFF Cup, khi Park Hang Seo c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 H\u1ed3 Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/tien-ve-hung-dung-lo-lang-ve-kha-nang-du-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng, t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, ch\u00e0ng &ldquo;th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng &ndash; b\u1edfi Mr. Park ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i. Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdn ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u cho t\u1edbi V-League, D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, song song v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian, s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng Park \u01b0u \u00e1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Thanh H\u00f3a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, v\u00e0 anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"V\u0103n L\u00e2m vs Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/vanlamdung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e0n em \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng anh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111i Indonesia v\u00ec &ldquo;\u0111en&rdquo;, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi anh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i hy sinh v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, v\u00e0 anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"V\u0103n L\u00e2m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/vanlam.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Park Hang Seo<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Park c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em theo th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c, th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 quan, b\u1edfi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam phong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, suy cho c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Park Hang Seo bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi&rdquo; th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ebfm hoi t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trong khung g\u1ed7, t\u00ednh trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c ASIAD. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng trang l\u1ee9a, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, khi chi\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. D\u00f9 sao, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Uzbekistan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang b\u00e0n t\u00e1n x\u00f4n xao v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi bi\u1ebft tin b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2118","checkdouble":"194022"},{"date":"07:17 08/08","title":"Sarri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9i thu cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/sarri-hua-hen-ngay-cuoi-chuyen-nhuong-boi-thu-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea. T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1ee7a The Blues chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 Kepa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kepa Arrizabalaga tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao. The Blues \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1ea1nh tay c\u1ee7a Chelsea sau khi Thibaut Courtois quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf 2 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p. Bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Courtois, Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi Kepa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean sau khi Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Lyon tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup (h\u00f2a 0-0 sau 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh), HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Kepa: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Kepa 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Napoli v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi d\u00f9 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Sarri mi\u1ec5n c\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois. &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5. T\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Lyon. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Courtois. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri\" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-maurizio-sarri-du-am-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh) b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n. &ldquo;T\u00f4i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y r\u1ea5t b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Kepa, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Eden Hazard. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Real Madrid ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho t\u1edbi khi k\u1ef3 mua s\u1eafm m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc-172-193892.html\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-courtois-va-hazard-cu-thoai-mai-ra-di-172-193879.html\">Sao Chelsea: &ldquo;Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-barca-172-193877.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2117","checkdouble":"193991"},{"date":"07:28 08/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8: Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-88-pogba-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Everton mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea. </strong>Everton \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kurt Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea. The Toffees \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Manchester United v\u00e0 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona song t\u1edbi nay ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U. </strong>Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward c\u1ee7a Man United r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barcelona. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Barca theo giao k\u00e8o c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 88 Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 88 Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Tien-ve-Paul-Pogba-tro-lai-MU-sau-ky-nghi-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Milan \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Bakayoko. </strong>AC Milan \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1eeb Chelsea. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 \u1edf Monaco. Anh hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng HLV Maurizio Sarri b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nCandreva t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Inter.</strong> Antonio Candreva \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Inter Milan. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 31 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Monaco. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng Keita Balde \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Lazio.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nTottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch sao tr\u1ebb Anh 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. </strong>Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a BBC, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Tottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch nhau 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Grealish. Spurs hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i Anh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00eam 9/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish cua Aston Villa\" title=\"Jack Grealish cua Aston Villa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/5-thuong-vu-sap-xay-ra-truoc-khi-ky-chuyen-nhuong-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Sao tr\u1ebb Chirivella chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Liverpool. </strong>Celtic hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Pedro Chirivella v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y, Rosenborg \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng Chirivella th\u00ec l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Na Uy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal tung chi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Dembele khi\u1ebfn Barca ng\u00e3 ng\u1eeda.</strong> Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Barca. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n mu\u1ed9n Dembele trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 9 c\u1ee7a West Ham \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Arsenal?</strong> Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Sky Sports kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2116","checkdouble":"193992"},{"date":"08:29 08/08","title":"AC Milan n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \"bom x\u1ecbt\" Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n San Siro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Bakayoko cho AC v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/AC-Mian-mua-Tiemoue-Bakayoko-bang-duoc-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Bakayoko v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tiemoue Bakayoko c\u1ee7a Chelsea, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o The Blues. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u1ef1u sao Monaco \u0111ang g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi Chelsea c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, song Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb. The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Bakayoko l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ac-milan-chi-30-trieu-bang-hoi-mua-bakayoko-172-192180.html\" target=\"_blank\">AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko </span>c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n San Siro. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko trong tran Chelsea 1-0 MU chung ket FA Cup 2017/18\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 MU chung k\u1ebft FA Cup 2017/18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Tiemoue Bakayoko l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ecf ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Bakayoko t\u1eeb Monaco, song v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb AC Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u01b0\u1ee3n. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bakayoko ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, AC s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Diadie Samassekou c\u1ee7a Red Bull Salzburg.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2115","checkdouble":"193993"},{"date":"08:43 08/08","title":"Rio Ferdinand lo s\u1ee3 MU s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/rio-ferdinand-lo-so-mu-se-that-bai-o-mua-giai-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang lo s\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf ch\u1eb7ng n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Man xanh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/rio-ferdinand-lo-so-mu-se-that-bai-o-mua-giai-201819.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i M.U m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, trong \u0111\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t Fred \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Mourinho r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u1ede \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rio Ferdinand lo s\u1ee3 MU s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang lo s\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rio Ferdinand ha thap nhieu cau thu Barca sau tran thua.\" title=\"Rio Ferdinand h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca sau tr\u1eadn thua.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/12/Ferdinand-chi-trich-HLV-Arsene-Wenger-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rio Ferdinand lo s\u1ee3 MU s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u phi\u1ec1n n\u00e3o xung quanh M.U v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Mourinho r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u01b0ng \u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 th\u00ec Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Man City th\u00ec v\u1eabn v\u1eady, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, c\u00f2n v\u1edbi Liverpool, v\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ra h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n M.U gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2114","checkdouble":"193994"},{"date":"23:43 07/08","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 Uzbekistan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Uzbekistan, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huy sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/8, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Uzbekistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ebb g\u00e3y c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 65 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. R\u1ea5t may Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huysau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huysau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-khen-ngoi-Duc-Huysau-tran-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Tri th\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb: \"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea1n. Ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park. H\u00f4m nay v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kh\u00ed h\u1eadu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 quen r\u1ed3i. Th\u1ee9 2, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p s\u00e1t nhanh, d\u00f9ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean l\u00e0m ch\u00fang ta b\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. Th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t r\u00f5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00f9i s\u00e2u, khi ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo. Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c ra kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m nh\u01b0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u00ec ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\u201d.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\">Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193970.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193970.html\">HLV U23 Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV U23 Uzbekistan, Nuraliev Dilshod \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu, HLV Park Hang Seo lo \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee7 quan</span><br />\r\nGi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn lo l\u1eafng khi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u1ee9c Huy l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. H\u00f4m nay c\u1eadu \u1ea5y chuy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t hay. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 \u0111i c\u00f3 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4i. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o v\u1eafng th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o. \u0110\u1ee9c Huy l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ea5y. Em \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng di ASIAD\", \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng, b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nhanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngang c\u01a1 nh\u01b0 Palestine. V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt CLB B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u00a0\u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Uzbekistan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2113","checkdouble":"193977"}]}